# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:16
translate chinese reba12_d1862604:

    # "My phone starts buzzing. Reba's calling."
    "我的手机开始震动。是丽贝卡打来的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:20
translate chinese reba12_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "喂？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:21
translate chinese reba12_46aee291:

    # rb "Hey, [pcname]! Do you want to go camping with me again?"
    rb "嘿，[pcname]！你想再跟我去露营吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:22
translate chinese reba12_e5d4ff71:

    # rb "Now that Mickey's in jail, I thought maybe we could have a camping trip with just me and you. Do it right, you know?"
    rb "既然米奇进监狱了，我想也许我们可以来一次只有你和我俩的露营。好好地去一趟，懂吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:28
translate chinese reba12_24d432d5:

    # rb "Oh okay."
    rb "哦，好的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:29
translate chinese reba12_98c9309b:

    # rb "Well, um... maybe next week then."
    rb "那个，嗯……那可能下周吧。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:30
translate chinese reba12_7a49d7a7:

    # pc "Okay, see you later, Reba."
    pc "好的，回头见，瑞芭。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:31
translate chinese reba12_2aeade94:

    # "We hang up and I go back to what I was doing."
    "我们挂了电话，我继续做手头的事。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:35
translate chinese reba12_b1ace31a:

    # rb "Yay!"
    rb "太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:36
translate chinese reba12_655d7cf0:

    # rb "I'll head over and pick you up now. Get ready!"
    rb "我这就过去接你。快准备好！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:37
translate chinese reba12_b56b8704:

    # rb "We're gonna have a great weekend!"
    rb "我们这个周末会玩得很开心！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:38
translate chinese reba12_4f71e606:

    # "We hang up the phone and I get my things ready to go on this camping trip. Spending the night with Reba, alone this time, sounds incredible."
    "挂断电话后，我收拾好东西准备去露营。这次能和丽芭单独过夜，听起来太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:42
translate chinese reba12_371c7789:

    # "A little while later, she picks me up and we start out towards the lake."
    "过了一会儿，她来接我，我们便动身前往湖边。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:43
translate chinese reba12_acd8e955:

    # rb "Oh man, this is gonna be fun! We can go fishing. Go swimming. You know, same stuff we did last time..."
    rb "天哪，这一定会很有趣！我们可以去钓鱼，去游泳。你知道的，和上次做的一样……"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:44
translate chinese reba12_3e721e5a:

    # rb "But this time, my dumb-butt brother won't be around and we can sleep in the same tent."
    rb "不过这次，我那个笨蛋哥哥不在，我们可以睡在同一个帐篷里。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:45
translate chinese reba12_b0435202:

    # pc "That sounds fun."
    pc "听起来真不错。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:46
translate chinese reba12_093850fa:

    # rb "Oh trust me, it will be."
    rb "哦，相信我，肯定会很棒的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:49
translate chinese reba12_6dd347be:

    # rb "First things first. Gotta catch dinner. I only brought drinks, so if we don't catch something, we're gonna be real hungry."
    rb "先解决正事。得钓点晚饭。我只带了饮料，所以如果钓不到鱼，我们会饿坏的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:50
translate chinese reba12_9bc959f2:

    # pc "Leave it to me. I'm basically an expert at this now."
    pc "交给我吧。我现在基本上算是这方面的专家了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:51
translate chinese reba12_bb40bd64:

    # rb "Oh yeah?"
    rb "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:54
translate chinese reba12_c1aab455:

    # rb "I've been thinking a lot about what I'm going to do."
    rb "我一直在想该怎么办。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:55
translate chinese reba12_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:56
translate chinese reba12_fe107a80:

    # rb "Well, I feel like I need to get away from my family some, or they're going to get me in trouble."
    rb "嗯，我觉得我得离家一段时间，不然他们会把我卷进麻烦里的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:57
translate chinese reba12_8511173a:

    # rb "I didn't tell you, but the police actually put me in a room and interrogated me. They thought that I might be involved with the whole meth ring with Mickey."
    rb "我没跟你说过，但警察真的把我关进房间审问了。他们以为我可能跟米奇的那个冰毒团伙有牵连。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:58
translate chinese reba12_73152f54:

    # rb "They yelled at me, threatened me... it was scary."
    rb "他们对我大吼大叫，还威胁我……真的很可怕。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:59
translate chinese reba12_89052a8b:

    # pc "I'm sorry. That's awful."
    pc "真抱歉。那太糟糕了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:60
translate chinese reba12_1f84cfdc:

    # rb "I feel like if I don't get away, I'm going to get caught up in something. Even with Mickey gone, I have other family - cousins, uncles... they're all involved in that stuff."
    rb "我觉得如果我不离开，迟早会卷入什么麻烦。就算米奇走了，我还有其他亲戚——表兄弟、叔叔们……他们全都参与那种勾当。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:61
translate chinese reba12_021a6b49:

    # rb "But I don't want to abandon Momma. She needs me."
    rb "但我不想抛下妈妈。她需要我。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:62
translate chinese reba12_ffad25e3:

    # rb "I just feel so trapped."
    rb "我真的觉得自己被困住了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:63
translate chinese reba12_08433d1a:

    # pc "I'm sorry. I wish I could do more to help. Anything you need, I'll be there. All you have to do is ask."
    pc "真抱歉。真希望我能多帮点忙。无论你需要什么，我都会在。只要开口就好。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:66
translate chinese reba12_54cd8555:

    # rb "Thanks, [pcname]. I don't mean to bring the mood down. I just have a lot of thoughts going through the ol' noggin today."
    rb "谢谢，[pcname]。我不是故意要扫兴的。只是今天脑子里想了太多事。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:67
translate chinese reba12_efe585eb:

    # pc "It's okay. My mood's not down. Being here with you is great."
    pc "没关系。我心情很好。能和你在一起真棒。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:68
translate chinese reba12_f053b562:

    # rb "Yeah it is. We're gonna have so much fun."
    rb "是啊。我们会玩得很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:71
translate chinese reba12_38b8e64d:

    # "Suddenly there's a tug on my line, and then, to my suprise, Reba's line pulls taut as well."
    "突然，我的鱼线被猛地一拉，接着，令我惊讶的是，瑞芭的鱼线也绷紧了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:72
translate chinese reba12_c1b627a1:

    # rb "We both got one!?"
    rb "我们俩都钓到一条了！？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:73
translate chinese reba12_186ced72:

    # pc "I guess!"
    pc "看来是这样！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:74
translate chinese reba12_7302dc6e:

    # rb "At the same time!? That's nuts!"
    rb "同时！？这也太不可思议了！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:77
translate chinese reba12_41524078:

    # rb "Aw, we're a couple, and it's like we caught a couple."
    rb "哎呀，我们是一对，感觉就像钓到了一对。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:78
translate chinese reba12_e3203266:

    # pc "That's kind of sweet."
    pc "这还挺甜蜜的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:79
translate chinese reba12_d69a39b4:

    # rb "Yeah! Now we're gonna gut 'em and eat 'em!"
    rb "是啊！现在我们要把它们处理好，然后吃掉！"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:80
translate chinese reba12_783e9cc8:

    # pc "Slightly less sweet now."
    pc "现在感觉没那么甜蜜了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:83
translate chinese reba12_82f12fea:

    # "She puts the fish on ice for later, and we go swimming for a while. Well, less swimming, and more just making out in the water."
    "她把鱼放进冰里留着待会儿吃，我们去水里游了一会儿。好吧，与其说是游泳，不如说是在水里亲热。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:84
translate chinese reba12_9d8aed59:

    # rb "I love the feeling of your body against mine."
    rb "我喜欢你的身体贴着我的感觉。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:85
translate chinese reba12_70608daa:

    # rb "You're so hard. I mean... your body, not your beanpole."
    rb "你硬得像块石头。我是说……你的身体，不是你那根竹竿。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:86
translate chinese reba12_f5ab279e:

    # rb "But I guess that is too."
    rb "不过我想那也是。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:87
translate chinese reba12_41f2b245:

    # pc "I love your body too, Reba."
    pc "我也爱你的身体，瑞芭。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:88
translate chinese reba12_5e33aa23:

    # rb "Yeah?"
    rb "是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:89
translate chinese reba12_90e1b3aa:

    # pc "Of course. You're gorgeous."
    pc "当然。你太美了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:92
translate chinese reba12_9bf1a694:

    # rb "I want to give you my virginity tonight, okay?"
    rb "今晚我想把我的初夜给你，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:93
translate chinese reba12_659c9116:

    # pc "Are you sure?"
    pc "你确定吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:94
translate chinese reba12_6f8fbc94:

    # rb "Definitely."
    rb "绝对确定。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:95
translate chinese reba12_303fb0ee:

    # rb "I know you're supposed to wait until you're married and everything, but that never made no dang sense to me."
    rb "我知道按理说应该等到结婚之后才行，但这对我来说从来都没什么道理。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:96
translate chinese reba12_30ea61c2:

    # rb "Like buying a car without test driving it first. It's just dumb."
    rb "就像买车却不先试驾一样。简直蠢透了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:97
translate chinese reba12_97f09515:

    # pc "I agree. I'd be very happy to test drive you."
    pc "我同意。我很乐意试驾你。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:98
translate chinese reba12_aaa21deb:

    # rb "You definitely know how to rev my engine."
    rb "你确实知道怎么让我心跳加速。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:99
translate chinese reba12_824e580b:

    # pc "I hope you like driving stick."
    pc "希望你喜欢开手动挡。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:100
translate chinese reba12_512b1c2d:

    # rb "I can't wait to feel you inside of me."
    rb "我等不及要感受你在我的身体里了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:101
translate chinese reba12_32775d9b:

    # pc "That's not a car euphemism."
    pc "这可不是什么汽车隐喻。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:102
translate chinese reba12_4a800564:

    # rb "Aw, shut up."
    rb "哎呀，别说了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:105
translate chinese reba12_864dc736:

    # "We hang out in the water for a while, making out, her body pressed up against mine."
    "我们在水里待了一会儿，亲热着，她的身体紧贴着我。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:108
translate chinese reba12_1ad7b4a6:

    # "Then we go for a little hike on a trail near the lake, just chatting and taking in the fresh air and beautiful scenery."
    "然后我们沿着湖边的步道散了会儿步，只是聊聊天，呼吸着新鲜空气，欣赏着美丽的景色。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:109
translate chinese reba12_06ab5688:

    # rb "This whole day feels like foreplay a bit, doesn't it?"
    rb "这一整天感觉有点像前戏，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:110
translate chinese reba12_b623c602:

    # pc "A little bit."
    pc "确实有点。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:111
translate chinese reba12_cec57123:

    # rb "It's hard for me to even wait 'til tonight for you to stick it in me, I want it so bad."
    rb "我甚至等不及今晚让你进入我，我太想要了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:112
translate chinese reba12_98b4fc31:

    # rb "But I want my first time to be under the moonlight."
    rb "但我希望我的第一次是在月光下。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:115
translate chinese reba12_43eacdc8:

    # "She pulls me to her and puts her lips against mine again."
    "她把我拉向她，再次将双唇贴上我的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:116
translate chinese reba12_ea92cdb5:

    # rb "I just can't stop kissin' you."
    rb "我就是停不下来亲你。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:117
translate chinese reba12_e55c3a89:

    # rb "You're so dang sexy."
    rb "你真是性感得要命。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:118
translate chinese reba12_e6e03a56:

    # pc "Me? You're making me so hard I'm gonna tear through my shorts."
    pc "我？是你让我硬得快要把短裤撑破了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:119
translate chinese reba12_16542d2d:

    # rb "Oh yeah? What do you want to do to me?"
    rb "哦，是吗？你想对我做什么？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:120
translate chinese reba12_63a712cd:

    # pc "I want to take your clothes off, wrap your legs around my waist, and fuck you against this tree."
    pc "我想脱掉你的衣服，让你双腿缠住我的腰，然后靠着这棵树干干你。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:121
translate chinese reba12_d5b4c15f:

    # rb "Dang, that's hot."
    rb "天啊，这太刺激了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:122
translate chinese reba12_9d112136:

    # rb "But you'll just have to wait. I'll be worth it, I promise."
    rb "但你得再等等。我会让你觉得值得的，我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:123
translate chinese reba12_6efb0260:

    # pc "Oh, I have no doubt about that."
    pc "哦，我对此毫不怀疑。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:126
translate chinese reba12_d515088e:

    # "We're barely able to pull ourselves off each other to continue our hike."
    "我们几乎无法从彼此身上挣脱，才勉强继续徒步。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:127
translate chinese reba12_4d304c86:

    # "She seems to want to constantly be touching me, and I don't mind that at all."
    "她似乎总想触碰我，而我一点也不介意。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:128
translate chinese reba12_8d5b9e2c:

    # "Fuck, the sun can't go down fast enough."
    "该死，太阳怎么还不快点落山。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:132
translate chinese reba12_60b482be:

    # "After the walk, we're both starving, so she cooks up the fish we caught earlier."
    "徒步结束后，我们俩都饿坏了，于是她把我们早些时候钓到的鱼做成了饭。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:133
translate chinese reba12_075a9e74:

    # pc "This is some of the best fish I've ever had."
    pc "这是我吃过最好吃的鱼之一。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:134
translate chinese reba12_30c602d4:

    # rb "Can't beat taking it straight from the water to your belly."
    rb "刚从水里捞出来就吃，简直无与伦比。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:135
translate chinese reba12_d403635e:

    # rb "Momma taught me how to do all this, back when she was younger and we used to come to the lake as a family."
    rb "这些都是妈妈教我的，那时她还年轻，我们一家人常来湖边。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:136
translate chinese reba12_54a57070:

    # pc "You miss that, huh?"
    pc "你怀念那段时光，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:137
translate chinese reba12_0fdf7ba8:

    # rb "Hm. It's hard to explain. It's not that I miss it. Like, I wouldn't want it to happen again now... things just aren't the same. But I have fond memories of it."
    rb "嗯。很难说清楚。倒不是说我怀念。比如，我现在也不想重温旧梦……毕竟一切都变了。但我对那段时光确实怀有美好的回忆。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:138
translate chinese reba12_77af2d11:

    # rb "I don't really know how to explain it. It was a good time, and I like thinking back on it, but I've moved on now and want to create new memories, like this one with you."
    rb "我真的不知道该怎么形容。那是一段美好的时光，我也喜欢回想它，但我已经向前看了，想创造新的回忆，就像现在和你一起的这段。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:139
translate chinese reba12_d83c8e41:

    # pc "I get that."
    pc "我懂。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:142
translate chinese reba12_a1d1762a:

    # rb "Do you have memories like that with your family?"
    rb "你和家人也有过那样的回忆吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:143
translate chinese reba12_e7a26415:

    # pc "Yeah a few. I was pretty young when my mom died, but I remember having a picnic at the lake once. This lake. Just a different area. The beach was more sandy."
    pc "有几段。我妈妈去世时我年纪还很小，但我记得有一次在湖边野餐。就是这个湖。 只是位置不太一样。那里的沙滩沙子更多。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:144
translate chinese reba12_233cca99:

    # pc "I must have been like four or five. But I remember sitting there, playing in the sand."
    pc "我当时大概四五岁吧。但我记得坐在那里，在沙子里玩耍。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:148
translate chinese reba12_928cef6f:

    # pc "My mom and dad were sitting nearby. Dad had his arms wrapped around her and she was kind of nuzzling her head against his arm."
    pc "我爸妈就坐在附近。爸爸搂着她，她把头轻轻靠在他的胳膊上。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:149
translate chinese reba12_e22e501c:

    # pc "I just sat nearby and watched them. And it made me happy."
    pc "我就坐在旁边看着他们。那让我很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:150
translate chinese reba12_e2cfe472:

    # pc "I remembered that image many times when I was growing up. That was what love looked like."
    pc "长大后，我无数次回想起那个画面。那便是爱的模样。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:151
translate chinese reba12_75a73755:

    # pc "I could see it between them like it was a real, visible, thing, you know?"
    pc "我能真切地看到他们之间的爱，就像它是一个真实可见的事物，懂吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:154
translate chinese reba12_8476930d:

    # rb "Yeah. I know what you mean."
    rb "嗯。我明白你的意思。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:155
translate chinese reba12_6e5ee1b9:

    # rb "Geez, you're going to make me cry with this stuff. It's too dang sweet."
    rb "天啊，你这样说真要让我哭了。这也太感人了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:156
translate chinese reba12_aa9ed4cf:

    # rb "Let's go watch the sunset."
    rb "我们去看看日落吧。"

