    # rb "I'm going to register for classes at the college for next semester."
    rb "我要去大学注册下学期的课程。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:415
translate chinese reba12_2abff043:

    # rb "And I'm going to move out of Momma's trailer."
    rb "而且我要搬出妈妈的拖车房。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:416
translate chinese reba12_3f76f001:

    # pc "That's pretty big."
    pc "这可是个大决定。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:417
translate chinese reba12_ef6c63db:

    # rb "Yeah, but I don't wanna live with Momma forever, you know. I want to get out."
    rb "是啊，但我不想一辈子都和妈妈住在一起，你知道的。我想搬出去。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:418
translate chinese reba12_bf5e9a57:

    # rb "Don't get me wrong. I love my Momma and I'm not going to abandon her."
    rb "别误会。我爱我的妈妈，我不会抛弃她的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:419
translate chinese reba12_2825dd21:

    # rb "She's a little ignorant, but I think it's because she's been in this life, around these people for so long, it kinda brainwashes you."
    rb "她有点无知，但我觉得是因为她过这种生活，和这些人待得太久了，这会让人被洗脑。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:420
translate chinese reba12_3c5715ca:

    # rb "But she's not a bad person. She's not mean, like Mickey."
    rb "但她不是坏人。她不像米奇那样刻薄。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:422
translate chinese reba12_d501d2b5:

    # rb "But I don't want to end up in the same situation as her. I don't want to be brainwashed. I feel like I need to get away before I'm stuck, like she is."
    rb "但我不想落得跟她一样的下场。我不想被洗脑。我觉得得趁还没像她那样被困住之前逃离这里。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:423
translate chinese reba12_c87f03d5:

    # pc "So what are you going to do?"
    pc "那你打算怎么办？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:424
translate chinese reba12_29f8f5e5:

    # rb "I'm not sure yet. But first, I'm going to look for a new place to live."
    rb "我还没想好。不过首先，我要找个新地方住。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:425
translate chinese reba12_ee1e56fb:

    # rb "It's just, everything is so expensive. I'm going to probably have to find a roommate."
    rb "只是，现在什么都太贵了。我可能得找个室友。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:430
translate chinese reba12_0688f356:

    # rb "Oh, no I couldn't do that."
    rb "哦，不行，我做不到。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:431
translate chinese reba12_1026817c:

    # rb "Not until we've at least been together for a while, you know?"
    rb "至少我们得先在一起一段时间，你知道的？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:432
translate chinese reba12_f9206098:

    # rb "What if I move in, then we find out that we just can't stand living together?"
    rb "如果我搬进去，结果发现我们根本无法忍受一起生活怎么办？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:433
translate chinese reba12_10bac07e:

    # rb "Then we'd break up and I'd have to move right back out again. I don't want that."
    rb "那我们就会分手，我又得马上搬出来。我不想那样。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:434
translate chinese reba12_18a73075:

    # rb "Let's give this a little time before we make a commitment like that."
    rb "在做出那种承诺之前，我们先给这段关系一点时间吧。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:435
translate chinese reba12_d64bc11a:

    # pc "That makes sense."
    pc "这很合理。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:438
translate chinese reba12_cad9c016:

    # rb "Oh really?"
    rb "哦，真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:439
translate chinese reba12_6c602202:

    # rb "That'd be great if you can find somebody. Just let me know."
    rb "如果你能找到人就太好了。记得告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:440
translate chinese reba12_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:442
translate chinese reba12_57522f14:

    # rb "Okay. Thanks, [pcname]."
    rb "好的。谢谢，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:445
translate chinese reba12_21ef4ef9:

    # rb "This feels good, having a direction, knowing what I'm gonna do next."
    rb "这种感觉真好，有了方向，知道接下来该做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:446
translate chinese reba12_0cd2ce02:

    # rb "For the first time ever, I feel like I'm free."
    rb "我第一次感觉自己如此自由。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:447
translate chinese reba12_6d9cb3c0:

    # rb "Come on, let's go for a swim."
    rb "来吧，我们去游泳。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:450
translate chinese reba12_c5082328:

    # "She grabs me and pulls me into the water, laughing."
    "她拉着我，笑着把我拖进水里。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:451
translate chinese reba12_4bd69acd:

    # rb "This might have been the best weekend in my life."
    rb "这可能是我人生中最棒的一个周末。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:452
translate chinese reba12_ff44ffe9:

    # rb "I feel like I have so much ahead of me."
    rb "我觉得未来还有无限可能。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:453
translate chinese reba12_6d77d7b6:

    # pc "I can't wait to see what you do next."
    pc "我迫不及待想看看你接下来会做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:456
translate chinese reba12_2fd1efe3:

    # "Soon we have to pack everything up and drive back to Skyhill and rejoin the real world."
    "很快我们就得收拾好一切，开车回斯凯希尔，重新回到现实世界。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:457
translate chinese reba12_40964823:

    # "But for now, floating on the water, with nobody else around, just Reba and me..."
    "但此刻，漂浮在水面上，周围空无一人，只有丽芭和我……"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:458
translate chinese reba12_8da04e53:

    # "It sort of feels like a dream."
    "这感觉就像一场梦。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:463
translate chinese reba12_56d85e11:

    # pc "Thanks for inviting me out, Reba. It was a great weekend."
    pc "谢谢你邀请我出来，丽芭。这真是个棒极了的周末。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:464
translate chinese reba12_440e3804:

    # rb "Yeah it was. We'll do a lot more... of all of that."
    rb "是啊，确实如此。我们以后还会做更多……像这样的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:465
translate chinese reba12_1065838b:

    # pc "I'm looking forward to it."
    pc "我期待着那一天。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:466
translate chinese reba12_ffe835b6:

    # rb "I'd spend today with you too, if I didn't have to go to work."
    rb "如果今天不用去上班，我也想和你一起度过。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:469
translate chinese reba12_be698222:

    # "I kiss her goodbye, thinking about all the other things I want to do with her."
    "我吻别她，脑海中盘旋着所有想和她一起做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:470
translate chinese reba12_7c4906ee:

    # "Then I get out and she drives away and I go back to my not-so-normal life."
    "随后我上岸，她开车离去，而我则回到了那并不寻常的生活。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:3
    old "After the meth ring is busted,"
    new "等那个制毒团伙被捣毁后，"

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:4
    old "Reba will call you on a Saturday morning and invite you camping."
    new "瑞芭会在周六早上给你打电话，邀请你去露营。"

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:427
    old "Come live with me"
    new "来和我一起住吧"

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:436
    old "I may know somebody"
    new "我可能认识个人"

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:441
    old "I'll keep an eye out"
    new "我会留意一下的"

